Package antsimulator.framework.event

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameEvent
    Represents any event that might take place, such as the user attempting to close the game or move a character.
    SceneChangeEvent
    Represents an event where the user wishes to change scenes.
    ZoomEvent
    Represents an event where the user zooms the camera.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GameEvent.Type
    Type of the event.
    SceneChangeEvent.Scene
    Name of the scene we are changing to.
